Home »   Online Only , Section 4A , Top Highlights » Watch: YouTube stars share advice on coming out Watch: YouTube stars share advice on coming out Posted by Steve Lee, Editor   Online Only , Section 4A , Top Highlights Friday, October 9th, 2015 
With National Coming Out Day just around the corner ( Oct.11 ) YouTube Content Creator Raymond Braun, alongside Aaron and Austin Rhodes, have prepared the ultimate coming out guide offering their best advice and personal experience. Watch above as Raymond and The Rhodes Bros breakdown the coming out process and provide a check-list of all things coming out to consider.
